</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-kYHfwS lkFAWj pf-221_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-222_">Developing and disseminating clinical guidelines - Creating evidence-based clinical guidelines and ensuring they are readily accessible to all healthcare professionals.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-224_">Fostering a culture of continuous learning - Encouraging healthcare professionals to engage in ongoing education and professional development to stay abreast of the latest evidence and best practices.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-226_">Implementing robust clinical audits - Conducting regular clinical audits to assess care effectiveness and identify improvement areas.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-228_">Engaging patients in their care - Involving patients in decisions about their care, ensuring treatments are tailored to their needs and preferences based on the best available evidence.
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah cpQDEO pf-230_">Leveraging technology - Utilising technology to support evidence-based practice, including clinical decision support systems that provide healthcare professionals with evidence-based guidance at the point of care.
</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-furwcr dAWGlU pf-232_ pf-r pf-c-cm pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-233_"><h3 tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-kHOZwM hRBLBR pf-234_">The road ahead - Challenges and opportunities
